# POXY Sky Design System (v2)

Consumer app rebrand. Reference mockups: `design/v2/`. Production tokens: `assets/poxy-sky/`.

## Source of truth

1. `design/v2/poxy-brand-guide.html` — tokens, logo, typography
2. `assets/poxy-sky/tokens.css` — production CSS variables
3. `DESIGN.md` — integration contract

**Do not** use legacy Stitch pink/mint/cyber-luxury palette for new UI.

## Brand

- Accent: **Sky `#60C2E0`** (scale `--sky-50` … `--sky-900`)
- Logo: **Card** mark via `--px-cardmask` / `.px-mark`
- Default theme: **light** (`data-theme="light"`)
- Theme key: `localStorage` → `poxy-sky-theme`
- Button text: **always white** on primary buttons (both themes)
- Light primary btn: `--sky-800`; dark primary btn: `--sky-500`

## Typography

- UI: `--px-font` (SF Pro / Inter / system-ui)
- Hashes, serials, codes: `--px-mono`
- Do not add Syne, DM Mono, or neon cyber fonts for new chrome

## Components

Use `assets/poxy-sky/components.css` classes:

- `.px-btn`, `.px-btn-primary`, `.px-btn-glass`
- `.px-glass`, `.px-panel`
- `.px-input`, `.px-field-label`
- `.px-mark` for logo

New screen-specific rules: `px-` prefix only.

## Layout targets

| Zone | Pattern |
|------|---------|
| Landing | Sticky glass nav, hero case float, sections in `poxy-landing.html` |
| Auth | Centered card, glow backdrop — `poxy-auth.html` |
| App | Left rail 74px + topbar — `poxy-dashboard.html` |
| Open | Box → full-screen generation ritual — not spin wheel |

## Rarity colors (v2 — locked)

```
Common #8A8F98 · Rare #60C2E0 · Epic #456DB0 · Legendary #E0A23C · Mythic #D9744F
```

## Animations

- Entry: `pxFadeUp` 0.35s `cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)`
- Hover lift: `translateY(-1px)` or `brightness(1.08)` on primary
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` and performance mode toggle
- Open ritual timings from `poxy-dashboard.html` — do not shorten for "snappiness"

## Admin panel

`admin-terminal.html` is **out of scope** — do not apply Sky tokens there.
